,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"預咗有咁嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈毛只會令旁人<br />\n覺得泛民係「另類獨裁」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"始於雨革大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"敢問現今本土派<br />\n當初有邊個唔係泛民支持者？<br />\n<br />\n點解當中咁多人背棄泛民<br />\n轉向支持本土派<br />\n係咪本土派有派蛇齋餅糉？<br />\n<br />\n點解到今時今日<br />\n泛民都仲係認為自己無錯<br />\n係真正民主鬥士<br />\n其他人就係鬼係中共間諜<br />\n繼而篤灰割蓆<br />\n<br />\n呢種唯我獨尊嘅心態<br />\n我真係接受唔到"},{"pid":"a3505282de77e7c0ede12f1433febbee549e8894","tid":590580,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"唔講得架樓主，快啲走我掩護你，你快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb5360d1a2138cda6d83776b637302c3bbfe7d6","tid":590580,"uid":101994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a3505282de77e7c0ede12f1433febbee549e8894","tid":590580,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"唔講得架樓主，快啲走我掩護你，你快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"你由得我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69deaf61895aa9c446ac867522935b42ef97b16","tid":590580,"uid":41901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7fba52c7cbec5d4b97506baa4b9eaeec6c4f7029","tid":590580,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"392123867048671a8f655e14cf1de643b8a36c23","tid":590580,"uid":10